com.percussion.services.contentmgr
Interface IPSNodeDefinition

All Superinterfaces:
IPSCatalogIdentifier, IPSCatalogItem, ItemDefinition, NodeDefinition, Serializable
public interface IPSNodeDefinition
extends NodeDefinition, IPSCatalogItem

Expanded JSR-170 node definition that allows data update, plus expanded information for Rhythmyx

Node def names are returned using JSR-170 names with a prepended "rx:" and embedded spaces converted to underscore characters. Those wishing to work with the "raw" names need to use the get and set internal name methods.

Author:
dougrand
